draw_text(info1_x, info1_y, "Russian folk songs are a living history of the\nRussian people, rich, vivid and truthful, revealing\ntheir way of life. Russian music often contains folk\nmelodies and folk elements or music of other ethnic\ngroups living in Russia, even in classical or\nmilitary pieces. Balalaikas and domras are\nvarieties of Russian stringed instruments that lend\nfolk music from this region distinct sound.");